Usage: Running experiement with the shell script.

1. install tqdm in venv for the better progress visualization

2. Go to the root directory (playground) and type in
   sh ./battle/experiement.sh agent0 agent1 agent2 agent3 num_times

The definiation of arguments

agent0 ~ agent3:
Choose four agents from below for the experiement battle
 SimpleAgent       : simple
 RandomAgent       : random
 IgnoreAgent       : ignore
 SimpleTeam        : simpleTeam
 Monte Carlo Avg   : mcts_avg
 Monte Carlo MinMax: mcts_minmax

nums_times: how many time you want to run the experiement.

We are focus on the win rate of the team [0, 2]
